-up to this stage" and "Buddha after Krshna is like going back from the lin=
ear progression of spirituality that the Avatars manifest one after the oth=
er upto Krshna".<br> <br>I want to emphatically disagree with this not=
ion that Dasavatars of a "linear progression of spirituality..upto Krshna".=
<br> <br>*        *  &nbs=
p;     *<br> <br>Each avatara represents an aspect=
 of Supreme in a perfected form.<br> <br>Maharshi Parasara equated das=
avataras with planets. For
 example, Rama, Krishna and
 Narasimha are Sun, =
Moon and Mars, respectively.<br> <br>We also
