oul, mind, energy/initiative/drive, learning spirit, wisdom/discrimination,=
 spirit of enjoyment/being happy, patience/discipline, spirit of innovation=
/breaking barriers and detachment (respectively).<br> <br>Correspondin=
gly, each avatara is an expression of that aspect of Supreme in a perfected=
 form. Each story is an example of how that aspect operates.<br> <br>L=
ord Rama's story is a perfected example of how soul operates. Lord Krishna'=
s story is a perfected example of how mind operates. Lord Vamana's story is=
 a perfected example of how wisdom/discrimination operates. Lord Narasimha'=
